snippet: Hunks of wreckage from the crash of Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 arrived Tuesday in the Netherlands as the Dutch government rejected a call to hand over the investigation of the disaster.
abstract: Pieces of wreckage from the crash of Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 arrive in the Netherlands as the Dutch government rejects call to hand over the investigation of the disaster to United Nations.
lead_paragraph: Hunks of wreckage from the crash of Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 arrived Tuesday in the Netherlands as the Dutch government rejected a call to hand over the investigation of the disaster.

headline.main: The Netherlands: Dutch Refuse Call to Hand Malaysia Jet Inquiry to U.N.
headline.print_headline: The Netherlands: Dutch Refuse Call to Hand Malaysia Jet Inquiry to U.N.
